10 Statement of purpose of bill as introduced: This bill proposes to authorize the
11 use of Class B(2) waters in the State for use by a hydroelectric power
12 generation facility with a proposed installed capacity of five megawatts or less.
13 The bill would also direct the Secretary of Natural Resources to amend the
14 Vermont Water Quality Standards to reflect the inclusion of hydroelectric
15 power generation facilities with a proposed installed capacity of five
16 megawatts or less as a suitable use of Class B(2) waters.
